STATE EX REL. ZANDER
v.
JUDGE, SUMMIT CTY. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS 2018-1198 Supreme Court of Ohio. December 24, 2018

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On appellant's motion to strike appellee's brief for want of timely service pursuant to S.Ct.Prac.R. 3.11(B). Motion denied. Appellant may file a reply brief within 14 days.
